snippet.title: Cupid Island - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW ON STEAM!
http://bit.ly/wishlist-cupid

Welcome to Cupid Island, a cute life simulator about bringing couples together and nurturing their relationships! As a Cupid, you'll discover many different couples and help their love stories. Build, customize and expand the Island using the Love, Joy and Passion produced by the lovely residents.

This is the first gameplay teaser for the game, currently being developed by Supernova Games.

JOIN OUR DISCORD:
https://discord.gg/KWQXYwKYMg

SOCIAL MEDIA:
https://twitter.com/cupidisland
https://instagram.com/cupidisland
